snippet.title: Battlefish TD Official Game Trailer
snippet.description:
Battlefish is the a fantasy strategic game in the genre of Tower Defense (TD). The Battlefish TD is published by TopsLiked Ltd. and +9 Games Studio. The Battlefish has won several game wards, Best game of Year 2016, Best Strategic Game Award, and 5 other awards. In this game Fish have become Zombies and attack players' lands, the player needs to defend the lands and not allowing the fish zombies and fish monsters pass the gates! Be careful, FISH ARE COMING!!!

Download from Google Play: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.plus9.battlefishtd
Official Page: http://www.topsliked.com/battlefish-published-by-topsliked-official-page
